name: Lume Frost Giant Herder
description:
A rare, substantiated rendering of a female Frost Giant in traditional shepherd garments, espying her Cerulean Mountain home. Note the proud, confident demeanor, the natural materials with ornate trimmings, and the imposing battle-staff, likely fashioned from an uprooted oak.

Read more about this majestic race, and the world they inhabit, below:
https://lumelibrary.com/index.php?title=Frost_Giants

digital inks, 2048x2048
